disinformation but also blamed - you guessed it - racism.\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3488, \"end\": 3490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4189524302503937e-25, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 3597, \"end\": 3619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\", \"score\": 0.9996408769317395, \"rank\": 0.000359252083527117, \"text\": \"Russian disinformation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_disinformation_in_the_post-Soviet_era\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other mainstream \\\"news\\\" media\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"the news profession\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"- racism\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another AP headline: \\\"For female athletes of color, scrutiny around gender rules and identity is part of a long trend.\\\"\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3671, \"end\": 3673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4189524302503937e-25, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3704}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"gender rules\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"identity\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"a long trend\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The article went on to say: \\\"Female athletes of color have historically faced disproportionate scrutiny and discrimination when it comes to sex testing and false accusations that they are male or transgender.\\\"\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The article\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"Female athletes\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3837}, {\"ngram\": \"disproportionate scrutiny\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3887}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3906}, {\"ngram\": \"sex testing\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3935}, {\"ngram\": \"false accusations\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it quoted - you guessed it again - a professor: \\\"Medical anthropologist Danyal Kade Doyle Griffiths, an adjunct professor with the City University of New York (said): 'These examples strike me as particular cases where racism and transphobia and intersex phobia are kind of inseparable.'\\\"\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4078, \"end\": 4082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kade\", \"score\": 0.9696024411917367, \"rank\": 0.03135053865020731, \"text\": \"Kade\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kade\"}, {\"begin\": 4083, \"end\": 4088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\", \"score\": 0.99999977550581, \"rank\": 2.2449433731916056e-07, \"text\": \"Doyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\"}, {\"begin\": 4229, \"end\": 4240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"transphobia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transphobia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an adjunct professor\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4119}, {\"ngram\": \"the City University\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4144}, {\"ngram\": \"New York\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4156}, {\"ngram\": \"These examples\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4180}, {\"ngram\": \"particular cases\", \"from\": 4194, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"intersex phobia\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The whole charge of AP and the professor is a falsehood.\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4309, \"end\": 4311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4189524302503937e-25, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The whole charge\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4305}, {\"ngram\": \"the professor\", \"from\": 4316, \"to\": 4329}, {\"ngram\": \"a falsehood\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"White biological men who claim to be female and compete against women are routinely attacked for cheating.\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"White biological men\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4366}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See, for example, an earlier column about the University of Pennsylvania swimmer Lia Thomas, who claims to be female and robs women of their swimming records.\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"an earlier column\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"Pennsylvania\", \"from\": 4513, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"female and robs women\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"their swimming records\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC also claimed Khelif was a victim: \\\"Algerian Imane Khelif won welterweight gold Friday \\u2026 overcoming a firestorm of questions from opponents wrongly questioning her gender.\\\"\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4613, \"end\": 4616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999915744411, \"rank\": 8.425633391039023e-09, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4652, \"end\": 4660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999596566438406, \"rank\": 4.033046950043872e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4636}, {\"ngram\": \"a victim\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4649}, {\"ngram\": \"welterweight gold\", \"from\": 4678, \"to\": 4695}, {\"ngram\": \"a firestorm\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4727}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 4731, \"to\": 4740}, {\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4755}, {\"ngram\": \"her gender\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one exposed the deceit of the IOC and the left-wing media as effectively as the women who were forced to fight against Khelif and Lin.\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4823, \"end\": 4826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2586976209111932e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"the deceit\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"the left-wing media\", \"from\": 4831, \"to\": 4850}, {\"ngram\": \"the women\", \"from\": 4869, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4918}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 4926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC itself reported the words of Mexico's Brianda Tamara after she fought Khelif in December 2022: \\\"When I fought her I felt very much out of my depth.\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4928, \"end\": 4931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999915744411, \"rank\": 8.425633391039023e-09, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 4961, \"end\": 4967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999998185230816, \"rank\": 1.814751724378636e-07, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 4978, \"end\": 4984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9999998816656513, \"rank\": 5.890354545201891e-08, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4957}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5008}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5020}, {\"ngram\": \"my depth\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her blows hurt me a lot, I do not think I had ever felt like that in my 13 years as a boxer, nor in my sparring with men.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her blows\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5090}, {\"ngram\": \"my 13 years\", \"from\": 5150, \"to\": 5161}, {\"ngram\": \"a boxer\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5172}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank God that day I got out of the ring safely.\\\"\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 5209, \"to\": 5212}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Essentially Sports reported that female boxer Svetlana Kamenova Staneva of Bulgaria, who lost her chance at a gold medal when she was defeated by Lin, refused \\\"to shake hands with Lin Yu Ting and instead (was) defiantly displaying an 'X' gesture in the ring, implying her XX chromosomes compared to her opponent's reported XY chromosomes.\\\"\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5329, \"end\": 5337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 4.8205132587633896e-12, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}, {\"begin\": 5526, \"end\": 5528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.974395400207883e-17, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"that female boxer\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5299}, {\"ngram\": \"Svetlana Kamenova Staneva\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5325}, {\"ngram\": \"her chance\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5358}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5374}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5403}, {\"ngram\": \"hands\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5428}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin Yu Ting\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'X\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5490}, {\"ngram\": \"' gesture\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5499}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5511}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent's reported XY chromosomes\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Turkish female boxer, Esra Yildiz Kahraman, also displayed an \\\"X\\\" gesture after Lin defeated her.\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5597, \"end\": 5604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\", \"score\": 0.8097729636387524, \"rank\": 0.23264606079357344, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 5624, \"end\": 5630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 2.7170099727708034e-11, \"text\": \"Yildiz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\"}, {\"begin\": 5631, \"end\": 5639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\", \"score\": 0.9101295171701695, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kahraman\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an \\\"X\\\" gesture\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5670}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Presumably, the IOC, AP, NBC and NewsGuard regard all these women fighters as sore losers.\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5712, \"end\": 5715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2586976209111932e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43