 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5806, \"to\": 5815}, {\"ngram\": \"her fight\", \"from\": 5866, \"to\": 5875}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 5887}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 5894, \"to\": 5909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sobbing at having to quit the fight, she later told the press: \\\"I am heartbroken.\", \"from\": 5911, \"to\": 5992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 5937, \"to\": 5946}, {\"ngram\": \"the press\", \"from\": 5963, \"to\": 5972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to the ring to honor my father.\", \"from\": 5993, \"to\": 6031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 6003, \"to\": 6011}, {\"ngram\": \"my father\", \"from\": 6021, \"to\": 6030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was often told that I was a warrior, but I preferred to stop for my health.\", \"from\": 6032, \"to\": 6109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warrior\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6069}, {\"ngram\": \"my health\", \"from\": 6099, \"to\": 6108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never felt a punch like this.\\\"\", \"from\": 6110, \"to\": 6147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a punch\", \"from\": 6128, \"to\": 6135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The solution is testing for chromosomes - not testosterone levels, not genitals, not self-identification.\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The solution\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6161}, {\"ngram\": \"chromosomes\", \"from\": 6177, \"to\": 6188}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone levels\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6214}, {\"ngram\": \"genitals\", \"from\": 6220, \"to\": 6228}, {\"ngram\": \"self-identification\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may well be that Khelif herself did not know until tested that she was a biological male.\", \"fr